# show-only-last-code-result

Use this CSS chunk with the slide `class: show-only-last-code-result`.

````
```{css echo=FALSE}
.show-only-last-code-result pre + pre:not(:last-of-type) code[class="remark-code"] {
	display: none;
}
```
````
